        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/ps-jan-3-1.jpg" alt="New Orleans attack" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; ">New Orleans remains in a somber state following its New Year’s <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-03-01-2025-h1-1-terrorist-attack" target="_blank">terrorist attack</a> just after many gathered in the French Quarter to ring in 2025. The FBI confirmed on Thursday that 14 people were killed. The attacker died during a shootout with police. Some of the <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-03-01-2025-h1-2-victims-were-identified" target="_blank">victims were identified</a>, and the information was released to the public.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4;filter: blur(5px)">The FBI states that the incident was inspired by the <a href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-03-01-2025-h1-3-islamic-state-group" target="_blank">Islamic State group</a>. They added that the attacker, Shamsud-Din Jabbar, posted videos on Facebook before the attack proclaiming his support for the militant group. The attack plans included the placement of crude bombs, which the officials have rendered safe. FBI branded the incident as an act of terrorism and confirmed that there was no connection between this incident and the Texas Cybertruck explosion.</p>
        </mj-text>
